    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独自一人，尽享MMORPG般的团队副本体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉寻找队友或等待公会的压力。在《Chaos Bringer》中，你将独自运用自己的战略才华，征服史诗级的团队副本首领。指挥你的8人英雄小队，按自己的方式取得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你是指挥官，是战场上的天才</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时暂停时间，预测敌人的下一步行动。向你的英雄下达完美的指令序列，看你无懈可击的计划完美展开。你的远见将扭转战局，通过时间轴系统组合技能，创造出如毁灭交响乐般强大无比的连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/144b8250b0dc4bc381a75d6392eb7f57.poster.avif?t=1768201641\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/144b8250b0dc4bc381a75d6392eb7f57.webm?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/144b8250b0dc4bc381a75d6392eb7f57.mp4?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与巨型团队副本首领展开惊心动魄的智谋对决</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受MMORPG的核心乐趣，现在专为单人玩家设计。面对拥有多样化、多阶段模式的强大首领，考验你的战术头脑。实时监控仇恨（TPS）和秒伤（DPS），完美控制战斗节奏，将伤害推向极限，同时保住你的坦克。每一秒都是惊险的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/f1f52364b92b61207e953637a80cfac1.poster.avif?t=1768201641\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/f1f52364b92b61207e953637a80cfac1.webm?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/f1f52364b92b61207e953637a80cfac1.mp4?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成长的每一刻都充满乐趣</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告别枯燥的“肝”。《Chaos Bringer》的每个部分都像一部巨大机器中相互关联的齿轮，不断为你提供新的目标和新的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/427616262ac0b071f7543ff5c4798f38.poster.avif?t=1768201641\" width=716 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/427616262ac0b071f7543ff5c4798f38.webm?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119830/extras/427616262ac0b071f7543ff5c4798f38.mp4?t=1768201641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. 探索：</strong>深入千变万化的Roguelike式地下城。体验快节奏的战略战斗，每一次冒险都是全新的刺激挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. 沉浸：</strong>你的旅程将跟随一条丰富而引人入胜的故事线。你不仅仅是在升级；你是塑造这个世界命运的主角。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. 创造：</strong>使用冒险中获得的材料，打造能完善你独特战略的定制装备。构筑一个专注于闪避而非标准防御的坦克，用你自己的创意构筑智取团队副本。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4. 征服：</strong>是时候证明你的成长了。最高的荣誉和史诗级装备只能在团队副本中获得。用你独特的构筑和精湛的指挥击败巨大的首领，成为传奇。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即加入愿望单，为你的传奇团队副本做好准备！</strong></p>",
